docs {
  Phase 4 wizard endpoints under /api/organization/settings/operating-scope.

  - 01 Preview ORGANIZATION → returns blockers/warnings.
  - 02 Apply STORE on partner → 403 (partner is locked to STORE).
  - 03 Verify audit log → after a successful apply, GET shows new entry.
}
